  "reviews": "\u201cThe brilliantly simple gameplay packs a hilarious level of challenge.\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://fanboydestroy.com/2016/08/24/switch-n-shoot-one-button-masterpiece-well-worth-your-two-bucks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >&quot;DESTROY ALL FANBOYS!&quot;</a></a><br><br>\u201cSwitch 'N' Shoot's simple premise is reason enough to give it a try, and chasing that elusive high score while climbing up the online leaderboards offers enough long-time motivation to keep you enthralled for a while.\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://indiegames.com/2016/09/we_only_got_one_button_to_save.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >IndieGames</a></a><br><br>\u201cThe game\u2019s a true test of snappy reflexes, enemy and movement anticipation, and making quick decisions about when to take risks and when to play it safe.\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.vgblogger.com/indie-quickie-switch-n-shoot/38433/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >VGBlogger</a></a><br>",
